title: Wakey Drivey
description: WakeyDrivey prevents accidents by detecting driver fatigue and sounding an alarm. It also includes a map with directions and nearby EV charging stations. The project integrated Python-based detection with a React frontend using WebSockets.

title: Gupiteer
description: GuPiTEER, an innovative platform with all-in-one access to a variety of GPT models, offers contextual chat history and a built-in validation system, empowering users with the future of generative AI.

title: CluturaLink
description: This a place where people can sign up and be connected with those in the same minority in that person's community. Once they have created a account, they can post about stories of their culture, receipts of their food back home.
